# Community Platform MVP — Cursor Rules

## Project overview

A private, approval-gated talent discovery platform for advertising, marketing, and technology professionals. Members can showcase skills, discover collaborators, and access exclusive opportunities. The core loop is **talent discovery**: search and filter a curated member directory to find the right person fast.

---

## Tech stack

| Layer | Choice |
|---|---|
| Framework | Next.js 14+ (App Router) |
| Database + Auth + Storage | Supabase |
| Hosting | Vercel |
| Styling | Tailwind CSS |
| Components | shadcn/ui |
| Email | Resend + React Email |
| Search | Postgres full-text search (`tsvector` + `pg_trgm`) |
| State | Zustand (client), TanStack Query (server state) |
| Forms | React Hook Form + Zod |
| Language | TypeScript (strict mode) |

